import {Dropdown as BDropdown} from 'react-bootstrap/Dropdown';
import {Toggle, Menu, Item} from 'react-bootstrap/Dropdown'

export default function Dropdown() {
    return <BDropdown>
        <Toggle variant="success" id="dropdown-basic">
            Dropdown Button
        </Toggle>
        <Menu>
            <Item href="#/action-1">Action</Item>
            <Item href="#/action-2">Another action</Item>
            <Item href="#/action-3">Something else</Item>
        </Menu>
    </BDropdown>
}
